gujarati.context:
A few ages ago, many ages later will be stirred; 
Words formulate in thought, and the place is known; 
No one wakes up in the body, without a force pulling him in that direction.

Here is the translation:

There came to Meghpuur from there I, met Muktaanand Swami there; 
They went then to Kachchadesh, gave good counsel to Deva's son.

Here is the translation:

Truth is spoken by Saint Dasna, says the one I have mentioned Brahmmahol; 
In that, I have got rid of deceit, and Shrikrishna has pleased Udhhav.

Here is the translation:

A true word will not be, why it will happen, at the end it will be true and I will believe; 
Those who are self-controlled, they have said this punishment for that.

After freedom, Anand gets the word; 
It becomes the bliss of many people; 
See, it's like the heaven, Kailas, Vaikunth; 
There is no falsehood that will not be realized.
